data.description: A cozy home with a convenient location! This two story home has three bedrooms, two full baths, living room with fireplace and a loft. Second floor has two bedrooms, one full bath, and the loft. Down stairs you have one bedroom, one full bath and the living area with fireplace. Plus a kitchen with island that opens to the dinette area. Fully landscaped, low maintance backyard(done last year), shed with foundation, refrigerated air and roof less than 2 yrs old.  To top it off, this home is literally across the street from Providence East, Behind starbucks and restaurants on 375. Quick access to FT. Bliss and Montana. Call to schedule your showing!
